      <title>独家：LME 价格接近历史新高吸引中国铜出口</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/near-record-high-lme-prices-magnet-chinese-copper-exports-2024-05-01/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三位业内消息人士称，中国铜生产商计划出口多达 10 万吨铜，为 12 年来的最大出口量，旨在为推动铜价创下历史新高的涨势降温，并增加订单量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/near-record-high-lme-prices-magnet-chinese-copper-exports-2024-05-01/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 12:34:45 GMT</pubDate>
